考特尼·洛芙 (Courtney Love) 在《狂野殖民者》安吉拉·麦克拉斯基 (Angela McCluskey) 去世后表示哀悼https://www.nme.com/news/music/courtney-love-pays-tribute-after-death-of-the-wild-colonials-angela-mccluskey-3604249?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=courtney-love-向野生殖民者死后致敬安吉拉·麦克卢斯基Max PilleyWed, 20 Mar 2024 11:45:15 +0000 Music NewsNews..IndieRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3604249 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/angela_mccluskey_courtney.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="安吉拉·麦克拉斯基和考特尼·洛芙" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/angela_mccluskey_courtney.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/angela_mccluskey_courtney-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/angela_mccluskey_courtney-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/angela_mccluskey_courtney-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/angela_mccluskey_courtney-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/angela_mccluskey_courtney-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>洛芙形容她的朋友“也许是世界上最美丽的声音”</p><p>考<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/courtney-love-pays-tribute-after-death-of-the-wild-colonials-angela-mccluskey-3604249">特尼·洛夫 (Courtney Love) 在《狂野殖民者》安吉拉·麦克拉斯基 (Angela McCluskey) 去世后致敬的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/angela_mccluskey_courtney.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="安吉拉·麦克拉斯基和考特尼·洛芙" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/angela_mccluskey_courtney.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/angela_mccluskey_courtney-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/angela_mccluskey_courtney-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/202